• Password: admin1pa55

PART C: Configure Server-Based AAA Authentication Using RADIUS 
on R3.
I.
STEP 1:
R3:
• R3 → Radius → Services → AAA → on
• Client name : R3
• Client ip : 192.168.3.1
• Secret : radiuspa55
• Server type : radius
II.
STEP 2:
R3 (CLI):
• en
• config
• R3(config)# username Admin3 secret admin3pa55
III.
STEP 3:
R3 (CLI):
• R3(config)# aaa new-model 
• R3(config)# aaa authentication login default group radius local
IV.
STEP 4:
R3 (CLI):
• R3(config)# line console 0
• R3(config-line)# login authentication local
V.
STEP 5:
R3 (CLI):
• end
• exit
VI.
STEP 6:
R3:
• Username: Admin3 
• Password: admin3pa55
